{lang-eng}Maranamu nundi pranamunu niratamu vidipimpanu dharalo
Jivincan karavulo mari sajivuluga nitimantulapai prabhu netram
Nilucunu nilakadaga yadarthula mora yehova vinulu vinunu vidaka sahanamuto{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Yehova netramulu edu jerubbabelu cetakani gundu nūlun
Santosincunu bahu menduganu mahimalo vesenu vinayamuga
Mandira punadini mugincunatani cetulu mudamuna jarugunidi daivatmace{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Daivasana peddala madhya campinatlunna sajiva gottepilla
Yesuni kannulu ninnu kanaga jivincucunnananu koninan
Mrtudave nivilalo davanaiyunna vatini sarididdu jagratta yesuni svaramu vinu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Madilo parama prabhuvunerugu yadardha hrdayula balaparaca
Prdivi lo payaninci cūdaga prabhudrsti yehovanu vidi vellenu asa siriya raju dariki
Mati tappi nivu madi vartincitivi idi modalu niku yuddhamule{/lang-eng}
